<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.1.7">
<l>vāyuḷ vaiyakaṅ kaṇṭa maṭanallā</l>
<l>rāyar puttira ṉalla ṉarunteyvam</l>
<l>pāya cīruṭaip paṇpuṭaip pālakaṉ</l>
<l>māya ṉeṉṟu makiḻntaṉar mātarē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The good woman who saw the worlds in [his] mouth,</l>
<l>[that] woman rejoiced, saying, “he is no son of a cowherd,</l>
<l>[he is] the great Lord, Māyaṉ, the child who has qualities</l>
<l>[and] a nature that is pleasing".</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
